{"tid":1392330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］有冇人答到我點解要塞地鐵","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:10.000Z","uid":7168,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b238c070ea04167ed81057e86ce32792d443c557","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"首先 我知好多人反對塞地鐵 聽過好多原因  <br />\n<br />\n但我想講下點解應該塞 （帶番個頭盔先 我反對塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n老實依家係香港 我淨係睇到攬炒依條路可以行<br />\n<br />\n［red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淨係講錢</span>[/red]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">地鐵：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fb4HhV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffb4HhV2.png&h=4da7cae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地鐵一日乘客量係 4,824(千） 人次<br />\n<br />\n咁我當番工時間係四分一人啦 <br />\n另外四分三係放工 同非上班時間 <br />\n <br />\n姐係有120萬人朝早要坐地鐵 <br />\n<br />\n因為塞鐵 地鐵要免費比人出閘 我當一人坐10蚊<br />\n冇左1,200萬 未計成本 波板糖人 接駁巴士 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人工：</span><br />\n730果日相信好多人都遲到 大家遲左幾多我唔知<br />\n我當3個鐘頭 人工值$200計好呢<br />\n<br />\n120萬人既3個鐘（200$）值幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係2.4億 2.4億呀 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知唔2.4億係咩錢 我知咁樣計係好多假設<br />\n我知d工作量都最後都係大家要做番 <br />\n我知地鐵收入來源唔係淨係靠果482萬人次<br />\n<br />\n但你諗下 如果個社會好似禁左個時間停止制 大家都番路到工 但人工又照出 成個香港又會蝕幾多 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家咁既情況 我都諗唔到有一個令香港政府收皮既方法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果有方法可以令香港蝕咁多錢 我好願意聽<br />\n<br />\n我知730有巴士司機唔收錢上人 其實都有用 <br />\n當然有巴打話老人飛 跳閘依d當然都有用 但又有幾多人做到<br />\n<br />\n遊行又行過 比狗打又打過 比黑社會撚又撚過<br />\n<br />\n要贏 一係大家勇武過對家 打撚爆黑警 再打撚爆辣殺老解 <br />\n但問心 有幾多個香港人準備好咁樣做？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （我知前線絕前有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n要和班非罷工 講真唔好話我睇死 你罷得幾多日 一日 兩日 <br />\n8月5罷完一日咁點 8月6又照番工？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5年前雨傘話左比大家聽 自動自覺去罷工只會比人當on9仔 我就係一個好例子 身邊個個番晒 <br />\n<br />\n我唔係要打沉大家 叫大家番工 係要大家諗清楚點樣可以令成件事行落去 <br />\n <br />\n阻香港人番工係死罪 我知 <br />\n係因為要扮勤力 有大有細要養 要升職上位加人工<br />\n<br />\n但香港要贏 一定要攬埋依班人落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTopwtq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTopwtq.png&h=3c03eec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想攬炒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 我代730阻到大家番工既人講聲對唔住<br />\n但我心底想講一句 你地冇做錯到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇計錯數 又唔知大家岩唔岩聽 歡迎屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb989a3c595db75070d9834885dff5cd1364af3","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8757399a68f54f5efc0e91d3ffc6f17da7053346","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9520850363ae023c869a3ab929556b6eb64b2e3c","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c67d50d0dd16aad4efd6b254ec8a52e9de9e1a","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6cb7c3ed620300fb35353922e4150941960c7d","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988c08b7d409ed7971b41309ff580631fcf70cbc","tid":1392330,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a50be4252981fea8e3ac802e9c723a5ceadd959b","tid":1392330,"uid":262526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6881066a42b18dac4d6749033ff5b17e290ad43b","tid":1392330,"uid":185991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"好多人都想罷工但係就唔夠膽<br />\n塞一塞可以助攻"},{"pid":"4d2c8ad50acb7da9f67e11995d3668954326a33d","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d02e790be8d456cf10ba205cb560b6c87b2276","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6881066a42b18dac4d6749033ff5b17e290ad43b","tid":1392330,"uid":185991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"好多人都想罷工但係就唔夠膽<br />\n塞一塞可以助攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09a9f65f554c0b3cc247929ee37b81bbe7356fc","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf56e211901056b6de037bb3c4a85f322941c17","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef7fb58360002fd5a9dc2cbc2b7119886c5814d","tid":1392330,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ab7f80e